                                    ></path>
                                </svg>
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
                                <p class="text-[10px] font-bold text-slate-500">
                                    WhatsApp â€¢ Baru saja
                                </p>
                                <p
                                    class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-800 truncate"
                                >
                                    Pembayaran SPP Ananda Budi Berhasil.
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Text Content -->
            <div class="lg:w-1/2">
                <span
                    class="text-indigo-600 font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest bg-indigo-50 px-4 py-1 rounded-full mb-4 inline-block"
                    >Portal Wali Murid</span
                >
                <h2
                    class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6 leading-tight"
                >
                    Pantau Keuangan Sekolah dari <span class="text-indigo-600"
                        >Genggaman</span
                    >.
                </h2>
                <p class="text-slate-600 text-lg mb-8 leading-relaxed">
                    Berikan kenyamanan maksimal bagi orang tua siswa. Tanpa
                    perlu antre di sekolah, tanpa perlu konfirmasi manual yang
                    ribet.
                </p>

                <ul class="space-y-6">
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-4 group">
                        <div
                            class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-indigo-50 text-indigo-600 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 group-hover:bg-indigo-600 group-hover:text-white transition-all duration-300"
                        >
                            <svg
                                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                                class="w-6 h-6"
                                fill="none"
                                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                                stroke="currentColor"
                            >
                                <path
                                    stroke-linecap="round"
                                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                                    stroke-width="2"
                                    d="M15 17h5l-1.405-1.405A2.032 2.032 0 0118 14.158V11a6.002 6.002 0 00-4-5.659V5a2 2 0 10-4 0v.341C7.67 6.165 6 8.388 6 11v3.159c0 .538-.214 1.055-.595 1.436L4 17h5m6 0v1a3 3 0 11-6 0v-1m6 0H9"
                                ></path>
                            </svg>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h4 class="font-bold text-slate-900 text-lg mb-1">
                                Notifikasi Tagihan Otomatis
                            </h4>
                            <p class="text-slate-500">
                                Pengingat tagihan dikirim langsung ke WhatsApp
                                sebelum jatuh tempo.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-4 group">
                        <div
                            class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-emerald-50 text-emerald-600 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 group-hover:bg-emerald-600 group-hover:text-white transition-all duration-300"
                        >
                            <svg
                                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                                class="w-6 h-6"
                                fill="none"
                                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                                stroke="currentColor"
                            >
                                <path
                                    stroke-linecap="round"
                                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                                    stroke-width="2"
                                    d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"
